<h1>Your Blinds Are On The Way! 🚚</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

<p>Fantastic news! Your freshly repaired blinds have been shipped and are on their way back to you.</p>

<div class="success-box">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #2e7d32;">📦 Shipped!</h3>
    <p><strong>Order #<%= String.pad_leading(to_string(@order.id), 6, "0") %></strong></p>
    <%= if @order.tracking_number do %>
        <%= if @order.carrier do %>
            <p><strong><%= String.upcase(@order.carrier) %> Tracking Number:</strong> <%= @order.tracking_number %></p>
            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 15px 0;">
                <a href="<%= get_tracking_url(@order.carrier, @order.tracking_number) %>" 
                   class="button button-primary" 
                   target="_blank" 
                   style="text-decoration: none;">
                    Track Your Package →
                </a>
            </p>
        <% else %>
            <p><strong>Tracking Number:</strong> <%= @order.tracking_number %></p>
        <% end %>
    <% else %>
        <p>Tracking information will be updated soon.</p>
    <% end %>
</div>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">🕐 Expected Delivery</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;"><%= expected_delivery(@order.service_level) %></p>
</div>

<h3>What We Did:</h3>
<ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
    <li>✅ <strong>Restrung</strong> your blinds with matching cord</li>
    <li>✅ <strong>Cleaned</strong> and inspected all components</li>
    <li>✅ <strong>Tested</strong> for smooth operation</li>
    <li>✅ <strong>Carefully packaged</strong> for safe delivery</li>
</ul>

<div class="highlight-box">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #856404;">🎁 Special Offer!</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Need another repair? Get <strong>10% off</strong> your next order with code <strong>REPEAT10</strong></p>
</div>

<p style="color: #666; font-style: italic;">
    We're confident you'll love how your blinds look and work. Thank you for choosing BlindShop!
</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
The BlindRestoration Team</p>
